ere orchestration is only\nallowed among a local cluster of radio units. The spectral efficiency (SE) is\neither considered as an optimization constraint for each user equipment or as a\nsum SE in the objective function. We develop several algorithms to solve the\nrespective end-to-end optimization problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Jan 2023 19:42:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
