-the-art methods using a synthetic dataset.\nFurthermore, we successfully apply our methodology to the study of the\ntransmission dynamics of COVID-19 in the Basque Country (Spain) for almost a\nyear, from mid February 2020 to the end of January 2021.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jan 2023 12:14:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
